text: == Events == *September 4 — Romulus Augustus is deposed by Odoacer. *August — The usurper Basiliscus is deposed and Zeno is restored as Eastern Roman Emperor. *Peter the Fuller is restored as Patriarch of Antioch. == Births == *Aryabhata, Indian mathematician and astronomer == Deaths == *August 28 — Flavius Orestes, master of soldiers of the Western Roman Empire *Emperor Xianwen of Northern Wei
